query:
UPDATE users
            SET satker_id = COALESCE($2, satker_id),
                rank_id = COALESCE($3, rank_id),
                nrp = COALESCE($4, nrp),
                full_name = COALESCE($5, full_name),
                email = COALESCE($6, email),
                phone = COALESCE($7, phone),
                updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1
